Package: sqlserverconnect
Title: Simple Helpers for Connecting to 'SQL Server'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Dave", "Rosenman", email =
        "dave.rosenman.data@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Lightweight helpers for connecting to Microsoft 'SQL
        Server' using 'DBI', 'odbc', and 'pool'. Provides simple
        wrappers for building connection arguments, establishing
        connections, and safely disconnecting.
